body.name: M.2 SSD Enclosure, 10Gbps USB 3.1 SSD Enclosure 6TB Capacity for 22x30 42 60 80MM SSD
features: Designed for NVME NGFF SSD: This M.2 SSD enclosure supports 22x30, 42, 60, 80MM NVME and NGFF SSD. Suitable for Win, for OS X Laptop, for Linux operating system.
High Speed: This M.2 SSD enclosure complies with UASP and TRIM function, supporting up to 10Gbps transmission and extending the service life of SSD.

Aluminium Alloy: This SSD enclosure adopts copper bars with holes on the PCBA board, aluminum alloy plate on one side and the thermal pads can ensure a perfect cooling performance for the M.2 adapter.
Type C Interface: This Type C SSD enclosure adopts Type C interface and USB 3.1 Gen 1 supports data transfer speeds of up to 10Gbps, suitable for computer and TV.
Tool Free Design: This NGFF NVME SSD enclosure adopts tool free design which allows for quick and easy installation in less than 3 minutes, saving your time and effort.
